text: saw "kingdoms" in a new draft

Actually we made our own variant for fun in Orlando. Curse of Karona. Basically its a seperate pile of cars full of gifts and curses. Once a turn at Soc speed you can pray to Karona and draw a card. If you draw a curse or negative effect, you have to take it and cast it on yourself. But you could get ramp/cards/etc. If you refuse to pray to Karona 3 times in a row, or 3 people neglect her...she comes out on your end step. Then everyone, EVERY turn, HAVE to pray to her until she leaves the field.

Gets really fun quick. Put a doomsday in it just to be mean.
